title: Tenderloin Steaks and Roasted Mushrooms with Balsamic-Glazed Arugula Salad and Roasted Potatoes
description: Find me in Firenze! This Italian-inspired steak dinner features crispy breadcrumb-coated mushrooms, Parmesan potatoes and a bright arugula salad drizzled with balsamic glaze.

